      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと早く目が覚めちゃったわね\nまぁ今日の収録は午前中だし、いっか",
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "さてと、遙子お手製の野菜たっぷりスムージーを\n飲んでお仕事に備えるとしますか",
      "startTime": 14.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14933.333333300003,
          "startTime": 29.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅーん……今、こっちから声がしたような……\nあ、いたいた、遙子さ～ん……",
      "startTime": 26.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
